Description: Powered by Frooition.com Haute stuff at cool prices Shop Categories GUCCI Brown Leather Briefcase ~ Unisex style! Item Description Gucci’s Brown Briefcase is a unisex style with a polished professional look! Made of grainy leather that holds its shape, there’s a zipped pocket on the back, while the flap on front has a gold push lock that can be locked or opened to two compartments lined in beige fabric with a zipped pocket in the back compartment, two pen holders and two slide pockets in the front, and a large zipped compartment for the divider. Coming with a shoulder strap, key, clochette, booklet and dustbag, there is wear on the hardware and light wear on the corners, as well as very small marks on the leather. With a drop of one and a half inches to the handle, this bag lets you know Gucci means business!
